displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Ludhiana, India.

highlights.text: Sidhu Moose Wala has the most spots on Top Songs Ludhiana. “Never Fold” is the highest at #13.
“On Top” by Karan Aujla has been on Top Songs Ludhiana the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
“Old Me” by Arjan Dhillon is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Ludhiana, up 35 spots at #45.
“Challa - Spotify Singles” by Gurdas Maan, Diljit Dosanjh, and Ikky is the highest new entry on Top Songs Ludhiana at #28.
